    <h2 style="margin-bottom:16px;">This is just the beginning.</h2>
    <p style="max-width:520px;margin:0 auto 32px;font-size:15px;font-weight:300;color:var(--slate);line-height:1.75;">Inset vs overlay cabinets. How heated floors actually work. Quartz vs granite without the sales pitch. What paint sheens actually mean. All of it — from the field.</p>
